# Git commit / push — always use the skill

When the user asks to **commit**, **push**, **save to GitHub**, or similar:

1. **Read and follow** `.assistant/skills/commit-to-github/SKILL.md` — it is the single source of truth.
2. **No git writes** until the user has approved the visual plan.
